# IO.NET

Use `io-net/<model>` with VoltAgent's model router.

## Quick start

```ts
import { Agent } from "@voltagent/core";

const agent = new Agent({
  name: "io-net-agent",
  instructions: "You are a helpful assistant",
  model: "io-net/Intel/Qwen3-Coder-480B-A35B-Instruct-int4-mixed-ar",
});
```

## Environment variables

- `IOINTELLIGENCE_API_KEY`

## Provider package

`@ai-sdk/openai-compatible`

This provider uses the OpenAI-compatible adapter.

## Default base URL

`https://api.intelligence.io.solutions/api/v1`

You can override the base URL by setting `IO_NET_BASE_URL`.
